### Aegis auth — request examples
### Run with the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client) or any HTTP client.
### Replace @host with your env: localhost:3000 or logistics.aegisfestival.com.

@host = http://localhost:3000
@email = booking@aegisfestival.com
@password = changeme-please-12345
@badPassword = nope

### Sign up — success (only works when NEXT_PUBLIC_ALLOW_SIGNUP=true)
# @name signup
POST {{host}}/api/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "name": "Eli"
}

### Sign up — failure: weak password (better-auth rejects < 8 chars)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "weak@example.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "name": "Weak"
}

### Sign up — failure: duplicate email
POST {{host}}/api/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "name": "Dup"
}

### Sign in — success
# @name signin
POST {{host}}/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Sign in — failure: wrong password
POST {{host}}/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{badPassword}}"
}

### Sign in — failure: unknown email
POST {{host}}/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ghost@example.com",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Get session — must run after sign-in (cookies must persist in client)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/get-session
Cookie: better-auth.session_token=...replace_with_cookie_from_signin...

### Sign out
POST {{host}}/api/auth/sign-out
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: better-auth.session_token=...replace_with_cookie_from_signin...
